{
  "id": "RAW_2c208f4f",
  "title": "我把 Claude Code 换成 GLM-4.7 用了 6 小时，我竟然没发现明显区别",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247500129&idx=1&sn=b61787da7f029c90163a6ad0e5f06149",
  "date": "2025-12-23 06:01:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2a602770&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F607DKnuWzlHt4LK1YKXoCszMJfiaqibSkiave8KHpUhPz1IIPT4ABtMYQMzHKFj7RloQbaJYRsuqFFNa7xBhph0Vw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">哈喽，大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM 4.7发布了，从客观数据看，编程方面进步很大。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">智谱可能是国内最早打“平替Claude”牌的AI厂商了，对于智谱的新模型，我也毫不犹豫用Claude Code来测试，看看这次平替能力是否进步了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">先说结论：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我把Claude Code换成 GLM-4.7 用了6小时，竟然没发现明显区别，最明显的区别是省钱了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">省流版</span></span></p>\n  <ol class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" start=\"1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">前端能力进步很大，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">审美极强</span>。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">用GLM-4.7驱动Claude Code<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">，中等难度以下任务，几乎感觉不到和原版有区别</span>。高难度任务（如：需要反复压缩上下文跨越多个上下文窗口的情况），能够看出来有区别，相比Claude Code原版更容易健忘。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">有点难以置信：在LMARENA的WebDev盲测榜中，GLM-4.7位列全球第六，甚至超过了GPT-5.2。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-4.7是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">开源</span>的，史上编程能力最强的开源模型！老外一定会深感震撼，按照某些美国明星科技企业的秉性，稍后等他们一起床，就会开始套壳了。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM Coding Plan 20人民币/月的套餐 值得购买，下文有二维码。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">小遗憾：暂时不是多模态（可以通过MCP来补）；上下文长度200K，属于中等长度。</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面我们稍微展开讲讲。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">如何在Claude Code里使用GLM 4.7？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-top: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">这里点赞一下智谱官方的贴心和专业。无论是Claude Code、还是Cline、Droid，所有开发者常用的工具，官方都做了教程。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/coding-plan/tool/claude-for-ide\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/coding-plan/tool/claude-for-ide</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016473\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6805555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e631f0d9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHt4LK1YKXoCszMJfiaqibSkiaBibV8iauicicttf5kXqQgziaiaZPBIQm1zm9MLpdIXclKK0XCD4c3xTM1q5g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-top: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-top: 8px; text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">我同时在Claude Code IDE插件、 Claude Code CLI、Droid、Cline里设置了GLM 4.7。四个方式我都感受了，我认为是在Claude Code IDE插件/Claude Code CLI里，GLM 4.7的体验最好。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016474\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4935185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f7146ec7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHt4LK1YKXoCszMJfiaqibSkiaQOxBeLaicuNemy4qCHyJvfS8tic9Dx1lzvtja45qRdKVBGfNVrb5TB4g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">前端能力进步很大</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在前两个月，但凡Google/OpenAI/Anthropic发布了新的模型，都会引入一个“金门大桥测试”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个测试非常难，以前用国产模型做，效果都不太好。因为这个任务还挺难的，是一个综合性特别强的任务，包括需要有世界知识、需要有物理知识、需要3D细节、可交互镜头、雨天地面湿润反光等等。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016470\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2196\" data-height=\"1372\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c8aea717&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHt4LK1YKXoCszMJfiaqibSkia9ulST599vPnq3Zefd1nPia4Y2eibma6DJpXaLZicUPvibj4ujicscCDibVCQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-4.7很争气，一次搞定。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过，可能是因为这个任务太难了，第一次做出来的时候，性能不是特别好。我再额外和GLM-4.7单聊了一会儿优化性能的事。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面请欣赏， GLM-4.7完成的金门大桥。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">怀疑作弊？我没有作弊，你可以复现！我来公布原始Prompt，你使用这一段Prompt，发给GLM-4.7，你也能得到同样的效果！ 震不震惊？</span></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"apache\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">ObjectiveBuild</span>&nbsp;a visually stunning, high-fidelity&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">3</span>D voxel-style simulation of the Golden Gate Bridge in Three.js.Prioritize complex visuals (not simple blocks), strong atmosphere depth, and smooth ~<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">60</span>FPS.Visuals &amp; Atmosphere- Lighting: a Time-of-day slider (<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">0</span>–<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">24</span>h) that controls sun position, intensity, sky color, and fog tint.- Fog: volumetric-feeling fog using lightweight sprite particles; slider&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">0</span>–<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">100</span>&nbsp;(<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">0</span>&nbsp;= crystal clear,&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">100</span>&nbsp;= dense but not pure whiteout).- Water: custom shader for waves + specular reflections; blend horizon with distance-based fog (exp2) so the far water merges naturally.- Post: ACES filmic tone mapping + optimized bloom (night lights glow but keep performance).Scene Details- Bridge: recognizable art-deco towers, main span cables + suspenders, piers/anchors consistent with suspension bridge structure.- Terrain: simple but convincing Marin Headlands + SF side peninsula silhouettes.- Skyline: procedural/instanced city blocks&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__literal\">on</span>&nbsp;the SF side to suggest depth.- Traffic: up to ~<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">400</span>&nbsp;cars via InstancedMesh, properly aligned&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__literal\">on</span>&nbsp;the deck (avoid clipping). Headlights/taillights emissive at night.- Ships: a few procedural cargo ships with navigation lights moving across the bay.- Nature: a small flock of animated birds (lightweight flocking).Night ModeAt night, enable city lights, bridge beacons, street lights, vehicle lights, ship nav lights.Tech &amp; Controls (Important)- Output MUST be a single self-contained HTML file (e.g., golden_gate_bridge.html) that runs by opening in Chrome.- No build tools (no Vite/Webpack). Pure HTML + JS.- Import Three.js and addons via CDN using ES Modules + importmap.- UI: nice-looking sliders for Time (<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">0</span>–<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">24</span>), Fog Density (<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">0</span>–<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">100</span>), Traffic Density (<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">0</span>–<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">100</span>), Camera Zoom.- Optimization: use InstancedMesh for repeated items (cars/lights/birds), avoid heavy geometry, keep draw calls low.</span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <pre style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><code data-lark-language=\"Markdown\" data-wrap=\"false\"></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们也可以顺便复习一下GPT-5.1的金门大桥。 &nbsp;是不是已经区别不大了？</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">LMARENA的WebDev盲测榜位列第六</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这可能是为数不多、不能刷的榜之一了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么？因为它没有标准答案，它是基于大规模的用户进行双盲测试。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在WebDev分类排名，在我印象中，似乎还没有国产模型排名如此靠前过，何况GLM-4.7还是个开源模型。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016468\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.026851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1272\" data-height=\"1306\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4dd220ef&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHt4LK1YKXoCszMJfiaqibSkiacZrOc4yWGbbYlACrFOPGR3uibh58mkKA8qsKHvB4u1ic3u06jwoDTv6w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">用GLM 4.7平替Claude Code，中等难度以下任务无感</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们一直在期待“无感平替”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们先简单闻闻味儿 —— &nbsp;下面两个图，你能看出这是GLM 4.7吗？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我用了一下午都没看出来！我以为它是原生的Claude Sonnet模型呢，无论是行文风格、代码逻辑、情绪价值，都很像。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016469\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6953703703703704\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2112\" data-height=\"1468\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a2e1db1e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHt4LK1YKXoCszMJfiaqibSkiaw3pYwzCZP6t0BjBkKp6kgU3gZIZ0sp9MlZEyUXT7lhZnJIV5GJYN7g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016467\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2094\" data-height=\"1466\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=621662ea&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHt4LK1YKXoCszMJfiaqibSkiaMDfwUB9BfAA8aU2HqwtP2DS6XEdBtdJSeQUNrkp4ahFKiaydEWiakLdg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">用GLM 4.7平替Claude Code，哪种任务会感觉有区别？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">经过不断上难度测试，我发现，当我们遇到「需要跨越很多个上下文窗口」的复杂任务的时候，能够看出来GLM 4.7是略逊于最顶级模型的，有点小遗憾。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">具体表现是：对于超复杂的长程任务，即便是事先写了特别长的文档，GLM-4.7也会偶发健忘，需要提醒。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是因为，Claude Sonnet 4.5、Claude Opus 4.5、GPT-5.2-Codex等等2025年9月以后出现的最顶级编程模型，都训练“原生长程能力”，能够更好的跨越多个上下文窗口。因此，你可能之前看到过有人提到，用这几款模型，能够“自己卷自己好几个小时”。国产模型在这方面的能力，还没有赶上，相信不远的将来（也许3个月内）就会赶上！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">好在，这样的任务并不多见，就算遇到了偶发健忘，也可以稍微多聊两句提醒提醒。 GLM 4.7 是目前国内最“无感平替”的Claude Code平替了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">如何在补齐GLM-4.7的多模态能力、联网搜索能力？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">GLM包月套餐里提供了联网搜索、多模态能力，作为MCP接入。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">详见这里&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/coding-plan/mcp/vision-mcp-server\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/coding-plan/mcp/vision-mcp-server</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016477\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42685185185185187\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2029402c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHt4LK1YKXoCszMJfiaqibSkia1ANpulQ6nMXuP8bUYLbu7ZicNicAD2uMcaocwfSic2odF5Dq4Rpw6iazGQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">以视觉理解为例，在命令行里执行一句命令，就添加好了</span></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"nginx\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">claude</span>&nbsp;mcp add -s user zai-mcp-server --env Z_AI_API_KEY=your_api_key -- npx -y&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\"><span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">@z_ai</span></span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">/mcp-server\"</span></span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016478\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.675\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2bcc1f56&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHt4LK1YKXoCszMJfiaqibSkiaD1RBNTcbYysD2T3ytFQfAXE2N8HgOES9q9N4hRWZeuhtnhicdI1af4A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">不仅可以看懂图片，还能分析视频内容呢。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016480\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5787037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7af2cd35&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHt4LK1YKXoCszMJfiaqibSkiaYPd9ZE5NzYtRz1W4Xz3yQ4VcyxdY5Micib5BicPECW1dp9k9v2PcXpF4A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">GLM</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">&nbsp;Coding Plan 包月套餐</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM Coding Plan仍然是良心价格。比20元/月更划算的是54元/季。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016471\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5444444444444444\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"3088\" data-height=\"1682\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4035872f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHt4LK1YKXoCszMJfiaqibSkiahib06jzgUOdNWoz6WW5icGCSgOUTM0QHS0YZheHhw2bc686acg6nby6g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以扫码购买试试看。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016472\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0448275862068965\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"580\" style=\"width: 229px;height: 239px;\" data-width=\"580\" data-height=\"606\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9df2f458&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHt4LK1YKXoCszMJfiaqibSkiaIuynZljJ3LRS0IQwVpVEztXh9tkUicIdhJI5SeL5dvka3v8f86HSWqw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">期待交流。</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "智谱 GLM-4.7 在编程能力上取得了显著进步，尤其在前端和中等难度任务中几乎可以“无感平替”Claude Code，且价格更低，但在长上下文处理上仍有改进空间。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "智谱 GLM-4.7 在编程能力上取得了显著进步，尤其在前端和中等难度任务中几乎可以“无感平替”Claude Code，且价格更低，但在长上下文处理上仍有改进空间。",
  "summary": "文章详细评测了智谱新发布的 GLM-4.7 模型在编程任务上的表现，特别是作为 Claude Code“平替”的可能性。作者通过实际使用 6 小时后发现，GLM-4.7 在中等难度以下任务中，体验与 Claude Code 几乎无异，尤其在前端能力和审美方面表现出色，甚至在 LMARENA 的 WebDev 盲测榜上排名全球第六。然而，在处理需要跨越多个上下文窗口的高难度任务时，GLM-4.7 偶有“健忘”现象，略逊于顶级模型。文章还介绍了如何在 Claude Code 中配置 GLM-4.7，并提及了其 Coding Plan 的亲民价格，以及通过 MCP 补齐多模态和联网搜索能力的方法。",
